# OneChat Gmail connector — your OWN Google OAuth client credentials.
# Create them (free) at https://console.cloud.google.com:
#   1. APIs & Services -> Enable "Gmail API"
#   2. APIs & Services -> Credentials -> Create OAuth client ID
#   3. Application type: "Desktop app"  (allows the localhost login below)
#   4. Add yourself as a Test user on the OAuth consent screen
# Copy this file to connectors/gmail/.env and fill in.
# NEVER commit .env or token.json — they authorize your account.

GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
